CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 29, 1958, pg. 6, reads: "'Main Street's' Four - Homewood Ave., the 'Main Street' which dissects the Homewood area, has several liquor dispensing establishments, including (top left picture): The 814 Bar in the 800 block... - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: 800 block of Homewood Avenue with 814 Bar, Brent's Dry Cleaners, and Belmar Theater advertising "Don't Go Near the Water" and "Last Hunt," Homewood
